00:44:40,079 --> 00:44:42,749
Maaf karena tadi aku emosi.

714
00:44:45,380 --> 00:44:46,450
Maafkan aku.

715
00:44:49,289 --> 00:44:52,320
Jadi, sekarang kamu mau membantuku?

716
00:44:52,720 --> 00:44:53,729
Ya.

717
00:44:54,360 --> 00:44:56,860
Aku juga punya kenalan.

718
00:44:56,959 --> 00:44:58,999
Aku bisa membagikan ini di media sosialku.

719
00:44:58,999 --> 00:45:00,769
Beritanya akan tersebar lebih cepat.

720
00:45:02,869 --> 00:45:03,939
"Korban pelecehan seksual dan pemecatan Geumjeong"

721
00:45:03,939 --> 00:45:05,539
"Tiga pengunjung"

722
00:45:08,970 --> 00:45:10,639
"11 pengunjung"

723
00:45:16,849 --> 00:45:17,849
Lihatlah.

724
00:45:17,849 --> 00:45:18,880
"53 pengunjung, 56 pengunjung"

725
00:45:18,880 --> 00:45:19,990
Berhasil.

726
00:45:21,189 --> 00:45:22,189
Tos.

