860
00:54:01,169 --> 00:54:02,840
- "Jadi..."
- Terlalu panjang.

861
00:54:03,309 --> 00:54:04,639
Dia akan memarahimu.

862
00:54:04,709 --> 00:54:06,610
Lalu? Dia mau atau tidak?

863
00:54:07,410 --> 00:54:08,450
Jadi...

864
00:54:09,110 --> 00:54:11,320
Dia mau bersaksi dan segera tiba di sini.

865
00:54:11,579 --> 00:54:12,680
Bagus.

866
00:54:13,189 --> 00:54:14,490
Hubungi mereka.

867
00:54:14,490 --> 00:54:16,119
Mari kita lihat reaksi mereka.

868
00:54:44,380 --> 00:54:46,079
Kamu bilang memahami perasaanku.

869
00:54:47,720 --> 00:54:49,019
Lantas kenapa dia...

870
00:54:49,650 --> 00:54:51,490
Begini...

871
00:54:51,490 --> 00:54:54,760
Nona Baek Eun Young, kamu bekerja selama enam bulan

872
00:54:54,860 --> 00:54:57,030
sejak bulan Maret hingga bulan September 2016.

873
00:54:57,999 --> 00:54:59,329
Sepertinya

874
00:54:59,329 --> 00:55:01,800
kamu tidak pernah bekerja di perusahaan lain.

875
00:55:02,200 --> 00:55:03,869
Benar.

876
00:55:04,240 --> 00:55:07,309
Sejak bulan Juni hingga bulan Agustus 2012

877
00:55:07,309 --> 00:55:10,410
