892
00:56:02,329 --> 00:56:03,329
Kang Seok.

893
00:56:04,030 --> 00:56:05,800
Tumben sekali.

894
00:56:05,800 --> 00:56:08,570
Kenapa kamu menangani kasus seperti ini?

895
00:56:33,760 --> 00:56:34,990
Nona Baek.

896
00:56:35,729 --> 00:56:37,099
Nona Baek, tunggu.

897
00:56:37,360 --> 00:56:39,300
Tunggu. Dengar...

